extends BasicPopupMenuSeparatorUI

    PopupMenuSeparatorUI实现类，默认是保持上下各1个像素的间距，这里设置为0。

    PopupMenu Separator UI implementation class, the default is to keep up and down the 1 pixel spacing, here is set to 0.
